OL,3,CPharmacies 'hanging on by their
OL,4,Cfingertips' with owners having to
OL,5,Cremortgage
OL,7,FSixty percent of pharmacy owners in
OL,8,FWales remortgaged their house or used
OL,9,Fpersonal savings to keep their doors
OL,10,Fopen last year, new research by the
OL,11,FNational Pharmacy Association (NPA)
OL,12,Fhas found.
OL,14,FGeoff Thomas, who runs two community
OL,15,Fpharmacies in Newport, has had to re-
OL,16,Ffinance in order to keep his
OL,17,Fbusinesses afloat.
OL,19,FHe explained that he is not alone in
OL,20,Ffeeling "a huge amount of stress" and
OL,21,Fwarned that he's at "a tipping point".
