OL,3,CPharmacies 'hanging on by their
OL,4,Cfingertips' with owners having to
OL,5,Cremortgage
OL,7,F"I had to take out a loan in September
OL,8,Fto get me through the month," he said.
OL,9,F"I had to refinance following that
OL,10,Floan because short-term finance loans
OL,11,Fare expensive, so I have been cobbling
OL,12,Ftogether funding to support what we do.
OL,14,F"In fact, I am 23 years into owning
OL,15,Fthis pharmacy and I now owe twice as
OL,16,Fmuch as I do when I first purchased it
OL,17,Fback in 2003 and that's not a fair
OL,18,Freturn on 20 years' worth of work."
