OL,3,CPharmacies 'hanging on by their
OL,4,Cfingertips' with owners having to
OL,5,Cremortgage
OL,7,FThe survey also revealed four in 10
OL,8,Fpharmacies in Wales were not
OL,9,Fprofitable in 2025, increasing the
OL,10,Frisk of closures and cutbacks.
OL,12,FGareth Jones, the NPA's director of
OL,13,Fpolicy, described community pharmacies
OL,14,Fas "hanging on by their fingertips"
OL,15,Fand reiterated the need for an "urgent
OL,16,Fstabilisation payment" from the NHS to
OL,17,Fensure services to patients can
OL,18,Fcontinue in their current capacity.
