OL,3,CPharmacies 'hanging on by their
OL,4,Cfingertips' with owners having to
OL,5,Cremortgage
OL,7,FHe said: "Costs are going up and
OL,8,Fpharmacy owners are really struggling
OL,9,Fto cope with that. We are seeing
OL,10,Fpharmacy owners having to think about
OL,11,Fwhether they can provide all the
OL,12,Fservices they currently provide...
OL,14,F"Certainly, in the last few years a
OL,15,Fnumber of pharmacies in Wales have
OL,16,Fclosed. The pharmacies get the
OL,17,Fmajority of their income for providing
OL,18,FNHS services, the funding provided by
OL,19,Fthe NHS has just not kept up with cost
OL,20,Fof running the service.
