OL,3,CPharmacies 'hanging on by their
OL,4,Cfingertips' with owners having to
OL,5,Cremortgage
OL,7,F"So there is a really serious risk now
OL,8,Fif Welsh Government doesn't step in
OL,9,Fthat actually pharmacies will close."
OL,11,FThe Welsh Government said it
OL,12,Frecognised community pharmacies are
OL,13,F"essential" but added it has made
OL,14,F"significant investment in the sector"
OL,15,Fand funding for community pharmacies
OL,16,Fhas increased by more than #40million
OL,17,Fsince 2017.
